[SPEAKER_01] Uzima neke stvari iz,

471
00:31:36,160 --> 00:31:37,400
[SPEAKER_01] da li su yoga ili tako nekako.

472
00:31:37,400 --> 00:31:39,019
[SPEAKER_01] Meditacije i slično.

473
00:31:39,240 --> 00:31:43,099
[SPEAKER_01] i uzima, šta je bilo?

474
00:31:43,099 --> 00:31:44,119
[SPEAKER_01] Sad nije bilo na vrhu jezika.

475
00:31:44,119 --> 00:31:45,559
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, e, Kabala.

476
00:31:45,559 --> 00:31:46,680
[SPEAKER_01] Kabala.

477
00:31:46,680 --> 00:31:49,220
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, Kabala, koliko sam ja upoznat,

478
00:31:49,220 --> 00:31:51,640
[SPEAKER_01] i to pričam iz laječke perspektive,

479
00:31:51,640 --> 00:31:55,099
[SPEAKER_01] koliko sam istraživo prije 15-20 godina.

480
00:31:57,099 --> 00:32:02,099
[SPEAKER_01] Uzmite u obzir da je sjećanje i vrijeme čini svoje.

481
00:32:02,099 --> 00:32:05,940
[SPEAKER_01] Na sjećanje, Kabala ima dva dijela.

482
00:32:05,940 --> 00:32:08,859
[SPEAKER_01] Takozvan teoretski i praktični dio.

483
00:32:08,859 --> 00:32:09,160
[SPEAKER_01] Dobro.

484
00:32:09,160 --> 00:32:12,119
[SPEAKER_01] Teoretski dio bih rekao da potencijalno

485
00:32:12,119 --> 00:32:13,160
[SPEAKER_01] nije možda problematičan.

486
00:32:13,160 --> 00:32:15,839
[SPEAKER_01] To više spada pod židovsku neku mistiku.

487
00:32:15,839 --> 00:32:16,319
[SPEAKER_01] Dobro.

488
00:32:16,319 --> 00:32:19,460
[SPEAKER_01] Praktični dio je prakticiranje te mistike

489
00:32:19,460 --> 00:32:20,700
[SPEAKER_01] kroz određene formule.

490
00:32:20,700 --> 00:32:25,319
[SPEAKER_01] Što je zapravo, skoro pa definicija magije.

491
00:32:25,920 --> 00:32:27,599
[SPEAKER_01] Definicija magije je, jak se ne varam,

492
00:32:27,599 --> 00:32:31,319
[SPEAKER_01] da pokušavaš kroz određene prakse

493
00:32:31,319 --> 00:32:36,059
[SPEAKER_01] utjecati preko duhovnog svijeta,

494
00:32:36,059 --> 00:32:37,859
[SPEAKER_01] utjecati na duhovni svijet,

495
00:32:37,859 --> 00:32:40,180
[SPEAKER_01] da stekneš nešto što želiš.

496
00:32:40,180 --> 00:32:41,640
[SPEAKER_01] Makar to bilo i dobro.

497
00:32:41,640 --> 00:32:43,779
[SPEAKER_01] I to katekizam isto kaže.

498
00:32:43,779 --> 00:32:44,940
[SPEAKER_00] Meni lajku.

499
00:32:44,940 --> 00:32:46,380
[SPEAKER_00] Kaj sam ja sad čuo svega ovoga?

500
00:32:46,380 --> 00:32:48,960
[SPEAKER_00] To znači da ja nešto što ne mogu

501
00:32:48,960 --> 00:32:51,640
[SPEAKER_00] na priroda način postić,

502
00:32:51,640 --> 00:32:53,160
[SPEAKER_00] makar to bilo i dobro,

503
00:32:53,160 --> 00:32:55,440
[SPEAKER_00] sa različitim formulama

504
00:32:55,440 --> 00:32:57,480
[SPEAKER_00] i praksama, radnjama, činima,

505
00:32:57,480 --> 00:32:59,299
[SPEAKER_00] da neki način to ostvarim.

506
00:32:59,299 --> 00:33:03,420
[SPEAKER_01] Da, ali bitan je ovaj dio između

507
00:33:03,420 --> 00:33:05,400
[SPEAKER_01] da kroz određene prakse radnje

508
00:33:05,400 --> 00:33:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] ulazim u duhovni svijet na neki način.

509
00:33:09,000 --> 00:33:10,460
[SPEAKER_01] Ja to ne mogu sam postić.

510
00:33:10,460 --> 00:33:14,319
[SPEAKER_01] Da, gdje se zazivaju neka, ajmo reći, druga božanstva.

511
00:33:14,319 --> 00:33:15,619
[SPEAKER_00] I to nije ta šuplja priča,

512
00:33:15,619 --> 00:33:16,980
[SPEAKER_00] kaj sam sad pitao ovo prije,

513
00:33:16,980 --> 00:33:18,579
[SPEAKER_00] to nije način šuplja priča bez pokriča,

514
00:33:18,579 --> 00:33:21,640
[SPEAKER_00] nego tu se nužan je taj duhovni svijet,

515
00:33:21,640 --> 00:33:23,400
[SPEAKER_00] druga nekakva...

516
00:33:23,400 --> 00:33:27,079
[SPEAKER_01] Da, katekizam čak u nekom trenutku

517
00:33:27,079 --> 00:33:28,480
[SPEAKER_01] kad priča o idolopoklonstvu,

518
00:33:28,480 --> 00:33:31,460
[SPEAKER_01] spominje da i u vjerničkom životu

519
00:33:31,460 --> 00:33:32,859
[SPEAKER_01] kao vjernici nismo izuzeti

520
00:33:32,859 --> 00:33:35,480
[SPEAKER_01] od opasnosti idolopoklonstva

521
00:33:35,480 --> 00:33:37,720
[SPEAKER_01] ili magijskog pristupa vjeri.

522
00:33:37,900 --> 00:33:39,779
[SPEAKER_01] Što bi značilo u prijevodu

523
00:33:39,779 --> 00:33:42,720
[SPEAKER_01] i nažalost, to mislim da se možemo

524
00:33:42,720 --> 00:33:43,519
[SPEAKER_01] poistavjetiti s time,

525
00:33:43,519 --> 00:33:46,799
[SPEAKER_01] nekad da imamo pristup,

526
00:33:46,799 --> 00:33:48,359
[SPEAKER_01] imam neki problem,

527
00:33:48,359 --> 00:33:49,980
[SPEAKER_01] izmoliću devetnicu

528
00:33:49,980 --> 00:33:51,559
[SPEAKER_01] i sigurno će se taj problem riješiti.

529
00:33:51,559 --> 00:33:53,720
[SPEAKER_01] Bože, ja tebi ovo, ti meni ovo.

530
00:33:53,720 --> 00:33:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sad, to je onaj trgovinski odnos s Bogom,

531
00:33:56,000 --> 00:33:59,019
[SPEAKER_01] gdje možemo mi imati kao magijski pristup,

532
00:33:59,019 --> 00:34:00,900
[SPEAKER_01] kao, e, ovo će sigurno pomoći.

533
00:34:00,900 --> 00:34:03,500
[SPEAKER_01] I mala je granica između,

534
00:34:03,500 --> 00:34:04,579
[SPEAKER_01] tanka je granica, ja bih rekao,

535
00:34:04,579 --> 00:34:07,539
[SPEAKER_01] između toga da kažeš nekom,

536
00:34:07,539 --> 00:34:09,099
[SPEAKER_01] e, meni je pomoglo kad sam to napravio,

537
00:34:09,099 --> 00:34:12,099
[SPEAKER_01] jer tu podrazumijeva nutarni stav srca.

538
00:34:12,099 --> 00:34:13,860
[SPEAKER_01] Da ja imam povjerenje u Boga

539
00:34:13,860 --> 00:34:14,900
[SPEAKER_01] koji će mi to ostvariti,

540
00:34:14,900 --> 00:34:15,880
[SPEAKER_01] po, recimo, zagovoru nekog sveca.

541
00:34:15,880 --> 00:34:17,500
[SPEAKER_01] Koji je dobri otak i koji će meni...

542
00:34:17,500 --> 00:34:19,579
[SPEAKER_01] Tako je, koji će i nagraditi.

543
00:34:19,579 --> 00:34:21,679
[SPEAKER_01] I ja mu se utječem po zagovoru,

544
00:34:21,679 --> 00:34:22,500
[SPEAKER_01] recimo, nekog sveca,

545
00:34:22,500 --> 00:34:23,400
[SPEAKER_01] kroz neku devetnicu,

546
00:34:23,400 --> 00:34:24,579
[SPEAKER_01] gdje izdvajam neko svoje vrijeme,

547
00:34:24,579 --> 00:34:27,199
[SPEAKER_01] dajem neku žrtvu, gospodinu,

548
00:34:27,199 --> 00:34:29,380
[SPEAKER_01] i gdje imam stav,

549
00:34:29,380 --> 00:34:31,159
[SPEAKER_01] ali ne moja, nego tvoja volja.

550
00:34:31,380 --> 00:34:32,559
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, ako je po tvojoj volji,

551
00:34:32,559 --> 00:34:33,860
[SPEAKER_01] onda ja bih tio to.

552
00:34:33,860 --> 00:34:34,960
[SPEAKER_01] Gdje se mi onda borimo,

553
00:34:34,960 --> 00:34:36,179
[SPEAKER_01] isto ulazimo u duhovni svijet,

554
00:34:36,179 --> 00:34:38,360
[SPEAKER_01] ali u jednom, potpuno drugom kontekstu.

555
00:34:38,360 --> 00:34:38,659
[SPEAKER_01] Koji želim?

556
00:34:38,659 --> 00:34:39,900
[SPEAKER_01] U ispravnom kontekstu,

557
00:34:39,900 --> 00:34:42,360
[SPEAKER_01] gdje uvažavamo Boga

558
00:34:42,360 --> 00:34:43,860
[SPEAKER_01] kao jedinog Boga.

559
00:34:43,860 --> 00:34:45,139
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, trojedinog Boga,

560
00:34:45,139 --> 00:34:46,539
[SPEAKER_01] Oca, Sina i Duha Svetoga,

561
00:34:46,539 --> 00:34:47,320
[SPEAKER_01] kao jedinog Boga,

562
00:34:47,320 --> 00:34:49,159
[SPEAKER_01] jedini koji je izvor svakog dobra.

563
00:34:49,159 --> 00:34:50,920
[SPEAKER_01] I onda se njemu utječemo

564
00:34:50,920 --> 00:34:53,099
[SPEAKER_01] da postignemo nešto.

565
00:34:53,099 --> 00:34:54,699
[SPEAKER_00] A magijski pristup bi znači,

566
00:34:54,699 --> 00:34:55,960
[SPEAKER_00] ok, ja ću to,

567
00:34:55,960 --> 00:34:57,500
[SPEAKER_00] znači, sve u mojim rukama,

568
00:34:57,500 --> 00:34:58,420
[SPEAKER_00] to je magijski pristup.

569
00:34:58,420 --> 00:35:00,780
[SPEAKER_00] Nema Bože jako je tvoja volja.

570
00:35:00,780 --> 00:35:02,119
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da, ne, to je moja.

571
00:35:02,119 --> 00:35:03,360
[SPEAKER_01] Ja to želim postići

572
00:35:03,360 --> 00:35:05,260
[SPEAKER_01] i ovo su prakse kojima ću ja to postići.

573
00:35:05,260 --> 00:35:07,280
[SPEAKER_01] Htio Bože ti to ili ne htio?

574
00:35:07,280 --> 00:35:07,960
[SPEAKER_01] Hvorilo, gvorilo.

575
00:35:07,960 --> 00:35:10,860
[SPEAKER_01] Ili zanemarajući opće Boga u cijeloj priči.

576
00:35:10,860 --> 00:35:13,059
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam ga, ja bih rekao,

577
00:35:13,059 --> 00:35:15,920
[SPEAKER_01] u svojim praksama nesvjesno zanemarivao,

578
00:35:16,059 --> 00:35:19,219
[SPEAKER_01] jer, kažem, nisam znao.

579
00:35:19,219 --> 00:35:19,500
[SPEAKER_01] Dobro.

580
00:35:19,500 --> 00:35:20,679
[SPEAKER_01] Tako ja bih rekao da puno ljudi

581
00:35:20,679 --> 00:35:21,619
[SPEAKER_01] koji su u tim praksama

582
00:35:21,619 --> 00:35:23,599
[SPEAKER_01] često ne znaju da čine zlo.

583
00:35:23,599 --> 00:35:25,099
[SPEAKER_01] Da ulaze u područje,

584
00:35:25,099 --> 00:35:27,099
[SPEAKER_01] da ih je džava jednostavno zavarao,

585
00:35:27,099 --> 00:35:29,420
[SPEAKER_01] ponudio im to kao nešto dobro,

586
00:35:29,420 --> 00:35:32,679
[SPEAKER_01] a možda jako bitan dio za nas kršćane,

587
00:35:32,679 --> 00:35:34,119
[SPEAKER_01] osobi to katolike koji gledamo,

588
00:35:34,119 --> 00:35:35,139
[SPEAKER_01] koji gledaju ovo,

589
00:35:35,139 --> 00:35:38,860
[SPEAKER_01] u nedostatku svjetlih primjera,

590
00:35:38,860 --> 00:35:40,039
[SPEAKER_01] svjedočanstva vjere.

591
00:35:40,039 --> 00:35:42,480
[SPEAKER_01] Znači ja sam poprlično siguran

592
00:35:42,480 --> 00:35:44,079
[SPEAKER_01] da je moj život potpuno drugačije izgledao

593
00:35:44,079 --> 00:35:45,219
[SPEAKER_01] da sam imao jednu osobu,

594
00:35:45,820 --> 00:35:47,340
[SPEAKER_01] samo jednu koja mi je bila dovoljno bliska,

595
00:35:47,340 --> 00:35:49,820
[SPEAKER_01] a koja je ozbiljno uzimala vjeru

596
00:35:49,820 --> 00:35:50,820
[SPEAKER_01] i živjela vjeru.

597
00:35:50,820 --> 00:35:51,760
[SPEAKER_01] Koja je molila za mene

598
00:35:51,760 --> 00:35:53,579
[SPEAKER_01] i kad sam zapravo se okružio ljudima

599
00:35:53,579 --> 00:35:54,940
[SPEAKER_01] koji su krenuli moliti za mene,

600
00:35:54,940 --> 00:35:56,079
[SPEAKER_01] koji su živjeli vjeru,

601
00:35:56,079 --> 00:35:57,440
[SPEAKER_01] to me privuklo jako.

602
00:35:57,440 --> 00:35:59,480
[SPEAKER_01] I to me izbavilo iz tih hralja

603
00:35:59,480 --> 00:36:00,800
[SPEAKER_01] do toga čemu doći.

604
00:36:00,800 --> 00:36:00,980
[SPEAKER_00] Ok.

605
00:36:00,980 --> 00:36:03,880
[SPEAKER_00] Zgoda sa egipatskim boženostvima.

606
00:36:03,880 --> 00:36:05,260
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim, koliko može biti zgoda?

607
00:36:05,260 --> 00:36:06,619
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da, nezgoda.

608
00:36:06,619 --> 00:36:09,300
[SPEAKER_01] Nezgodna zgoda, zvana nezgoda.

609
00:36:12,179 --> 00:36:12,920
[SPEAKER_01] Postoje jedno,

610
00:36:12,920 --> 00:36:15,380
[SPEAKER_01] postoje dva Hermesa

611
00:36:15,380 --> 00:36:18,480
[SPEAKER_01] u kontekstu božanstava.

612
00:36:18,480 --> 00:36:20,260
[SPEAKER_01] Možemo reći demona, ali božanstava.

613
00:36:20,260 --> 00:36:20,500
[SPEAKER_01] Dobro.

614
00:36:20,500 --> 00:36:21,780
[SPEAKER_01] Jedan je grčki Hermes.

615
00:36:21,780 --> 00:36:22,380
[SPEAKER_01] Dobro.

616
00:36:22,760 --> 00:36:26,460
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim da on bio nešto,

617
00:36:26,460 --> 00:36:27,699
[SPEAKER_01] glasnik neki, tako nešto.

618
00:36:27,699 --> 00:36:27,980
[SPEAKER_01] Dobro.

619
00:36:27,980 --> 00:36:29,780
[SPEAKER_01] I ima egipatski Hermes.

620
00:36:29,780 --> 00:36:32,280
[SPEAKER_01] Tako zvani Hermes Trismegistos.

621
00:36:32,280 --> 00:36:34,059
[SPEAKER_01] Tri puta najveći Hermes.

622
00:36:34,059 --> 00:36:34,400
[SPEAKER_01] Dobro.

623
00:36:34,400 --> 00:36:38,300
[SPEAKER_01] Tako se naziva, kao, jel?

624
00:36:38,300 --> 00:36:42,500
[SPEAKER_01] I on je bio kao bog psihičke magije.

625
00:36:42,500 --> 00:36:43,679
[SPEAKER_01] Tako je me zanimalo, jel?

626
00:36:43,679 --> 00:36:44,119
[SPEAKER_01] Dobro.

627
00:36:44,119 --> 00:36:45,559
[SPEAKER_01] Zadužen za psihičku magiju u Egiptu, jel?

628
00:36:47,500 --> 00:36:52,239
[SPEAKER_01] I on mi je bio od tih božanstava i tih nekih stvari,

629
00:36:52,239 --> 00:36:54,159
[SPEAKER_01] Bož mi prosti, najdražiji.

630
00:36:54,159 --> 00:36:56,659
[SPEAKER_01] U smislu, najviše sam se njemu utjecao.

631
00:36:56,659 --> 00:37:00,940
[SPEAKER_01] To je prakse koje njega spominju ulazi u to.

632
00:37:00,940 --> 00:37:05,940
[SPEAKER_01] I ja sam se obratio, znači, 2010. godine.

633
00:37:05,940 --> 00:37:08,139
[SPEAKER_01] I dubio ću vam pričati o tome, ali...

634
00:37:08,139 --> 00:37:11,239
[SPEAKER_01] Na katoličanstvo, da, da, da.

635
00:37:11,239 --> 00:37:15,659
[SPEAKER_01] Na kršćanstvo, pa katoličanstvo, možemo i o tome.

636
00:37:15,659 --> 00:37:17,760
[SPEAKER_01] Koliko si rekao, pet sati treba podkast?

637
00:37:17,760 --> 00:37:18,380
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da, pet.

638
00:37:18,380 --> 00:37:21,900
[SPEAKER_00] Obično pet, to je prosjek, da treba možemo i duže.

639
00:37:21,900 --> 00:37:22,420
[SPEAKER_01] E, dobro.

640
00:37:22,420 --> 00:37:23,599
[SPEAKER_01] Probat ćemo ajde upljati.

641
00:37:23,599 --> 00:37:23,880
[SPEAKER_01] Dobro.

642
00:37:23,880 --> 00:37:30,920
[SPEAKER_01] I bio sam, već sam tad ušao u zajednstvu na novorođeni.

643
00:37:30,920 --> 00:37:32,420
[SPEAKER_01] Bio sam jedno na molitvi.

644
00:37:32,420 --> 00:37:33,500
[SPEAKER_01] Čekaj, čekaj, čekaj, čekaj.

645
00:37:33,500 --> 00:37:37,980
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, obratio sam se na kršćanstvo, pa poslije katoličanstvo.

646
00:37:38,039 --> 00:37:39,380
[SPEAKER_01] Pa prošlo je još pet godina.

647
00:37:39,380 --> 00:37:45,380
[SPEAKER_01] I onda sam došao na molitvu kod velečasnog Ivice i Matije našeg.

648
00:37:45,380 --> 00:37:47,880
[SPEAKER_01] I još je bila i stana.

649
00:37:47,880 --> 00:37:51,480
[SPEAKER_01] I molili su za mene po fazama života.

650
00:37:51,480 --> 00:37:55,199
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim da je sati nešto trala molitva, gdje su u redom molili.

651
00:37:55,199 --> 00:37:57,480
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim da smo došli do rođenja, nismo došli dalje.

652
00:37:57,480 --> 00:38:00,440
[SPEAKER_01] Inače, preporučam svima, molitva po fazama života,

653
00:38:00,440 --> 00:38:03,340
[SPEAKER_01] bilo polazlje osobno ili uz neće vodstvo.

654
00:38:03,340 --> 00:38:06,280
[SPEAKER_01] Mio Barada najviše to propagira.

655
00:38:07,940 --> 00:38:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] I prolazili su tako, molili su za mene, kao zagovorna molitva,

656
00:38:12,000 --> 00:38:15,320
[SPEAKER_01] gdje smo prolazili po fazama života.

657
00:38:15,320 --> 00:38:18,320
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, od mog začeća, pa preko prvi mjesec, utrudnoći,

658
00:38:18,320 --> 00:38:19,599
[SPEAKER_01] mamin, drugi, treći i tako.

659
00:38:19,599 --> 00:38:21,079
[SPEAKER_01] I sve do rođenja.

660
00:38:21,079 --> 00:38:25,280
[SPEAKER_01] I u jednom trenutku Matija, koji ima jako izražen dar spoznaje,

661
00:38:25,280 --> 00:38:27,099
[SPEAKER_01] je zastoj rekao je,

662
00:38:28,099 --> 00:38:30,599
[SPEAKER_01] osjećam da nešto blokira molitvu.

663
00:38:30,599 --> 00:38:35,739
[SPEAKER_01] Nešto mi je kao neki trisim ego, trimi sego.

664
00:38:35,739 --> 00:38:37,480
[SPEAKER_01] Ja kažem, možda trismegistos.

665
